{"title":"一个老桥梁工","authors":["洪洋"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":10,"day":15}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个老桥梁工"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洪洋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"声音若宏钟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"豪语壮山河；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人问你一生修了多少桥？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“大、小何止三百座”！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第一辆列车从桥上过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车外波涛涌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你脸上皱纹一重重，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重重皱纹中，笑意生。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“虽说三百多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抵不了这一座！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说罢扬头向窗外，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车声轰隆隆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“这座大铁桥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好比我们新中国；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又高又长又坚牢！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最伟大！最美！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别看我头发白，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是新中国的青年；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要发奋来修桥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"修到共产主义的彼岸。”"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}